//- Render the title of a doclet.
//- For doclets rendered as a child of another one (e.g., a method within a class), the heading level is lowered from 3 to 4.
//- If the item has a type (e.g., "function", "variable", "class"), the type is displayed before the name of the item.
//- @param {SpacedocDoclet} item - Full doclet definition.
//- @param {?Boolean} sub - If doclet is a child of another.
mixin title(item, sub)
  - const tag = sub ? 'h4': 'h3';
  if item.meta.type
    #{tag} #{item.meta.type}: #{item.meta.name}
  else
    #{tag} item.meta.name
